        "description": "Man Group Chief Market Strategist Kristina Hooper is worried about how high energy costs are impacting consumers. She says oil at $120 or $130 could trigger a recession in the US. She speaks on Bloomberg The Close. Brent crude settled above $100 a barrel Thursday for the first time since August 2022. (Source: Bloomberg)",
